Stack Technique
 
Backend (Python/FastAPI)
 
framework: FastAPI
ml_framework: PyTorch, Ultralytics (YOLO)
model_serving: TorchServe, ONNX Runtime
database: 
  - PostgreSQL (données structurées)
  - Redis (cache/sessions)
  - MinIO (stockage images)
 
Application Flutter (Mobile + Web)
 
framework: Flutter 3.0+
state_management: Riverpod/Bloc
navigation: GoRouter/AutoRoute
http_client: Dio
local_storage: Hive/SharedPreferences
camera: camera package + image_picker
ml_inference: tflite_flutter / onnx_runtime
notifications: firebase_messaging / local_notifications
ui_framework: Flutter Material 3 + custom themes
charts: fl_chart / syncfusion_flutter_charts
